snippet.title: Announcement Trailer For a New Upcoming Game From genDESIGN | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
From the legendary studio behind Ico, Shadow of the Colossus, and The Last Guardian comes a new upcoming game. Debuted at The Game Awards 2024 you can keep up with the latest in development via their social channels:

#ps5 #ps5games #tga2024
